00196 void ArrayAttributesTest::testproperty_Attributes()
00197 {
00198         ArrayAttributes atts;
00199         ParameterNameValuePairVector &params = atts.Attributes();
00200         ParameterNameValuePair param;
00201 
00202         param.Name = L"array-att-name-1";
00203         param.Value = L"array-att-value-1";
00204         params.push_back(param);
00205 
00206         param.Name = L"array-att-name-2";
00207         param.Value = L"array-att-value-2";
00208         params.push_back(param);
00209 
00210         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( params.size() == 2 );
00211 
00212         ParameterNameValuePairVector::iterator it = atts.Attributes().begin();
00213         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).Name == L"array-att-name-1" );
00214         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).Value == L"array-att-value-1" );
00215         ++it;
00216         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).Name == L"array-att-name-2" );
00217         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).Value == L"array-att-value-2" );
00218         ++it;
00219         CPPUNIT_ASSERT (it == atts.Attributes().end() );
00220 
00221         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( atts.Attributes()[0].Name == L"array-att-name-1" );
00222         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( atts.Attributes()[0].Value == L"array-att-value-1" );
00223         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( atts.Attributes()[1].Name == L"array-att-name-2" );
00224         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( atts.Attributes()[1].Value == L"array-att-value-2" );
00225 }
